com.nokia.maps.map

Class Point

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nokia.maps.map.Point

  • public class Point
extends java.lang.Object
    The Point class is a pixel representation of a point in the view.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      Point()
      This method instantiates a new Point object with both x and y set to -1.
